</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Wedding_favors\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wedding favors\">Wedding favors</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Wedding_mandap\" title=\"Wedding mandap\">Wedding mandap</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Wedding_ring_cushion\" title=\"Wedding ring cushion\">Wedding ring cushion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Wishing_well_(wedding)\" title=\"Wishing well (wedding)\">Wishing well</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_wedding_ceremony_participants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"List of wedding ceremony participants\">Participants</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Bride\" title=\"Bride\">Bride</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_child_brides\" title=\"List of child brides\">child bride</a></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Bridegroom\" title=\"Bridegroom\">Bridegroom</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_child_bridegrooms\" title=\"List of child bridegrooms\">child bridegroom</a></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Bridesmaid\" title=\"Bridesmaid\">Bridesmaid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Bridesman\" title=\"Bridesman\">Bridesman</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Flower_girl\" title=\"Flower girl\">Flower girl</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Groomsman\" title=\"Groomsman\">Groomsman</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Page_boy_(wedding_attendant)\" title=\"Page boy (wedding attendant)\">Page boy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Marriage_officiant\" title=\"Marriage officiant\">Officiant</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Traditions</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Ahesta_Bero\" title=\"Ahes